description:
iOS has a 5-second timeout to hide loading indicator if messages don't arrive (ConversationView.swift:706-714):
```swift
DispatchQueue.main.asyncAfter(deadline: .now() + 5) {
    if self.isLoadingMessages {
        self.isLoadingMessages = false
    }
}
```

This prevents indefinite loading state on subscription failures. RN is missing this fallback - could hang in loading state if subscription fails.

Reference: ios/VoiceCode/Views/ConversationView.swift lines 706-714
